# Interactive Help Messages

Help.IconBar:\TPegs application.|MIt plays the Peg Solitaire board game.|M\Sstart a new game.

Help.Main:\Tmain Pegs \w.|MIt plays the game of Peg Solitaire, where the aim is to clear pegs from the board until only one is left.
Help.Main.Grid:\Dmove a counter.|MMoves or horizontal or vertical, and consist of a jump over a single hole containing a peg and landing in an empty hole.|MThe jumped peg is then removed.

Help.Info:\Tprogram information \w for the Pegs application.
Help.Info.Website:\Tprogram information \w for the Pegs application.|M\Svisit its website for information and updates.

Help.MainMenu.00:\Sstart a new game.

Help.IconBarMenu.00:\Rto see information about Pegs and visit its website.
Help.IconBarMenu.01:\Sread the Pegs documentation.
Help.IconBarMenu.02:\Stoggle whether or not drags in the Soliataire window use a representation of a peg or a dashed box.
Help.IconBarMenu.03:\Squit Soliatire.


